1. add customMessages to true:
   $.webshims.setOptions('forms', { customMessages: true });
or (better for performance but messages are not ready on DOM-ready):
$.webshims.setOptions('forms', { lazyCustomMessages: true });
1. replace native UI with custom UI
There are a lot of ways to do this. The most easiest way is by config:
$.webshims.setOptions('forms', { replaceValidationUI: true });
If you want to see a specific language you should set activeLang:
webshims.activeLang('ja');
All config should be called before you invoke the webshims.polyfill method.
